+
+  ----------------------------------------------- tiara
+  Tiara LanCard of Tiara Computer Systems.
+
+  +----------------------------------------------+
+  !           ! Transmitter Unit !               !
+  !           +------------------+             -------
+  !          MEM                              Coax Connector
+  !  ROM    7654321 <- I/O                     -------
+  !  :  :   +--------+                           !
+  !  :  :   ! 90C66LJ!                         +++
+  !  :  :   !        !                         !D  Switch to set
+  !  :  :   !        !                         !I  the Nodenumber
+  !  :  :   +--------+                         !P
+  !                                            !++
+  !         234567 <- IRQ                      !
+  +------------!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!--------+
+	       !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
+
+- 0 = Jumper Installed
+- 1 = Open
 
